@startuml
title UC-2 Merchant-presented Mode Payment - Customer Scans Merchant QR
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam dpi 140
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam titleFontSize 15
skinparam legendFontSize 10
skinparam participantFontSize 11
skinparam actorFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowFontSize 10
skinparam ArrowColor #4A5568
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #5B6B82
skinparam ActorBorderColor #5B6B82

legend right
|= Color |= System |
|<#FFF2CC>| Consumer / Merchant |
|<#D4F1EA>| Your POS / QR display |
|<#CFE2FF>| Your Backend / ACQP |
|<#F4CCCC>| Alipay+ backend |
|<#E1D5E7>| MPP Wallet |
----
|<#2F80ED>| Blue arrows = Alipay+ SDK / checkout calls |
|<#C0392B>| Red arrows = Alipay+ backend API calls |
|<#4A5568>| Gray arrows = non-Alipay API / SDK steps |
endlegend

actor Consumer #FFF2CC
actor "Store Cashier" as Cashier #FFF2CC
participant "Your POS / QR Display" as POS #D4F1EA
participant "Your Backend / ACQP" as ACQP #CFE2FF
participant "Alipay+ Backend" as AP #F4CCCC
participant "MPP Wallet" as Wallet #E1D5E7

autonumber "S00"

Cashier -> POS: Create order / amount
alt Entry code
  POS --> Consumer: Show ACQP-issued static entry QR
  note over POS
  Merchant-presented means the store shows the QR.
  It does not mean Alipay+ always generates the QR.
  end note
  Consumer -> Wallet: Scan merchant QR
  Wallet -> ACQP: Open merchant page URL in entry QR
  ACQP --> Consumer: Render merchant page / amount entry
  Consumer -> ACQP: Enter amount and confirm
  ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: pay(entry code scenario)
  AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: payment accepted / paymentUrl
  ACQP -[#2F80ED]--> Wallet: Redirect to payment confirmation page
else Order code
  POS -> ACQP: Create dynamic order
  ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: pay(order code scenario)
  AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: Alipay+-issued order code
  ACQP --> POS: Sync order QR to store
  POS --> Consumer: Show dynamic order QR
  Consumer -> Wallet: Scan merchant QR
  Wallet -> AP: Decode order code
else Private order code
  POS -> ACQP: Create dynamic order
  ACQP --> POS: Return ACQP-issued private QR
  POS --> Consumer: Show private order QR
  Consumer -> Wallet: Scan merchant QR
  Wallet -> AP: Decode private code
  AP -[#C0392B]> ACQP: userInitiatedPay(decode request)
  ACQP -[#C0392B]--> AP: Return merchant/order details
end

Wallet -> Consumer: Show payment confirmation
Consumer -> Wallet: Confirm / authenticate
Wallet --> AP: Payment result
AP -[#C0392B]> ACQP: notifyPayment(final status)
ACQP -[#C0392B]--> AP: SUCCESS ack
opt Callback missing or status still uncertain
  ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: inquiryPayment(paymentRequestId or paymentId)
  AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: paymentResult S, F, or U
end
ACQP --> POS: Payment result
POS --> Cashier: Show success / fail / pending
Cashier --> Consumer: Complete sale
@enduml
